      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "LAST TOUR (6) fifth-up for this and back in trip last start with a disappointing fifth to the smart Tannin over 1200m at Gosford from the rails draw. Key jockey change and assess on his earlier runs. Can finish over the top of these. ORANGE TSUNAMI (3) found them too sharp first-up with the 59kg when seventh over 1100m at Gosford. Lee Magorrian sticks and not without each-way prospects over the extra ground. PROXIMA CENTAURI (7) failed to come up in three runs in her first prep and returns from a lengthy break. Comes here with the two trials under the belt and expecting a better showing this time in. GONDORFF (2) jumped at long odds at debut and ran accordingly when sixth over 1100m here. Extra trip in his favour and can take a hand in the finish.",
